{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"PerformanceNavigation","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigation","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigation_timing_API\">Navigation timing API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigation\"><code>PerformanceNavigation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigation/redirectCount\"><code>redirectCount</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigation/type\"><code>type</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Navigation Timing</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Performance\"><code>Performance</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigationTiming\"><code>PerformanceNavigationTiming</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming\"><code>PerformanceTiming</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/performance_property\"><code>performance_property</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Summary","isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>PerformanceNavigation</code></strong><code>接口呈现了如何导航到当前文档的信息。</code></p>\n\n<p>这个类型的对象可以被只读属性<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Performance/navigation\"><code>Performance.navigation</code></a>调用。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em><code>PerformanceNavigation</code> 接口不继承任何属性。</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"performancenavigation.type_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigation/type\"><code>PerformanceNavigation.type</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>一个无符号短整型，表示是如何导航到这个页面的。可能的值如下：\n <dl>\n  <dt id=\"type_navigate\"><code>TYPE_NAVIGATE</code> (0)</dt>\n  <dd>当前页面是通过点击链接，书签和表单提交，或者脚本操作，或者在 url 中直接输入地址，type 值为 0</dd>\n  <dt id=\"type_reload\"><code>TYPE_RELOAD</code> (1)</dt>\n  <dd>点击刷新页面按钮或者通过<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Location/reload\"><code>Location.reload()</code></a>方法显示的页面，type 值为 1</dd>\n  <dd>The page was accessed by clicking the Reload button or via the <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Location/reload\"><code>Location.reload()</code></a> method.</dd>\n  <dt id=\"type_back_forward\"><code>TYPE_BACK_FORWARD</code> (2)</dt>\n  <dd>页面通过历史记录和前进后退访问时。type 值为 2</dd>\n  <dt id=\"type_reserved\"><code>TYPE_RESERVED</code> (255)</dt>\n  <dd>任何其他方式，type 值为 255</dd>\n </dl>\n </dd>\n <dt id=\"performancenavigation.redirectcount_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigation/redirectCount\"><code>PerformanceNavigation.redirectCount</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>无符号短整型，表示在到达这个页面之前重定向了多少次。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Methods","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em><em><code>Performance</code>&nbsp;接口没有继承任何方法</em></em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"performancenavigation.tojson\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>PerformanceNavigation.toJSON()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>把<code>PerformanceNavigation</code>转换成 JSON 对象</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/navigation-timing/#sec-navigation-info-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Navigation Timing<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">PerformanceNavigation</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.PerformanceNavigation","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigation/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>The <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Performance\"><code>Performance</code></a> that allows access to an object of this type.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigationTiming\"><code>PerformanceNavigationTiming</code></a> (part of Navigation Timing Level 2) <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Summary","id":"summary"},{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Methods","id":"methods"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"PerformanceNavigation接口呈现了如何导航到当前文档的信息。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"PerformanceNavigation","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"PerformanceNavigation","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"PerformanceNavigation","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"PerformanceNavigation","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/performancenavigation","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/performancenavigation/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigation","title":"PerformanceNavigation"}],"pageTitle":"PerformanceNavigation - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}